<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="">
  <head>
    <%- include('../partials/head') %>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/mentor.css" />
  </head>

  <style>
    #drop {
      font-family: Verdana, Geneva, Tahoma, sans-serif;
      margin: 20px auto;
      border: 1px solid #8080805c;
      padding: 12px 5px;
      width: 100%;
      float: left;
      color: #829da2;
      widows: 100%;
    }

    #etc {
      font-family: Verdana, Geneva, Tahoma, sans-serif;
      margin: 20px auto;
      border: 1px solid #8080805c;
      padding: 12px 5px;
      width: 100%;
      float: left;
      color: #829da2;
      widows: 100%;
      height: 300;
    }

    .info {
      font-weight: bold;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: red;
    }

    label {
      padding: 4px 2px;
      width: 100%;
    }
    input[type="submit"],
    input[type="dropuser"] {
      text-align: center;
      border: 1px solid #8080805c;
      width: 80%;
      padding: 12px 5px;
      margin: 20px auto;
      color: #829da2;
      cursor: pointer;
      float: left;
    }

    input[type="text"] {
      text-align: left;
      border: 1px solid #8080805c;
      width: 100%;
      padding: 12px 5px;
      margin: 20px auto;
      color: #829da2;
      float: left;
      cursor: auto;
    }

    input[name="dropuser"] {
      width: 20%;
      float: left;
    }

    input[type="file"] {
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
      width: 100%;
    }

    .content {
      width: 66%;
      float: left;
    }
    .profile {
      width: 80%;
      display: inline-block;
    }

    .image {
      margin: 20px auto;
      width: 25%;
      height: 25%;
      float: right;
      margin-right: 15%;
    }

    .button {
      margin: 0 auto;
      width: 100%;
      float: right;
    }

    .kind ul {
      background-color: #efefef;
      overflow: hidden;
      list-style-type: none;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    .kind li {
      float: left;
      width: 40%;
    }

    .kind li a {
      display: block;
      background-color: #efefef;
      color: #000000;
      text-align: center;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    .kind li a.current {
      background-color: #efefef;
      color: white;
    }

    .kind li a:hover:not(.current) {
      background-color: #cd853f;
      color: white;
    }

    #preview {
      background-color: aquamarine;
    }

    #btn {
      color: #829da2;
      background-color: #dbe5e7;
      border: 1px solid #8080805c;
    }
    #btn:hover {
      color: #dbe5e7;
      background-color: inherit;
      color: black;
      border: 1px solid black;
    }
  </style>

  <body id="top">
    <!-- Top Background Image Wrapper -->
    <div
      class="bgded overlay"
      style="background-image: url('/images/lighthouse.jpg')"
    >
      <%- include('../partials/nav') %>

      <div id="breadcrumb" class="hoc clear">
        <h6 class="heading">마이 페이지</h6>
        <br />
        <ul>
          <li><a href="/index">메인</a></li>
          <li><a href="#">마이 페이지</a></li>
          <li><a href="/mypage/mentee">멘티 정보</a></li>
          <li><a href="/mypage/mentee">대학생/취준생</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
    <!-- End Top Background Image Wrapper -->
    <div class="wrapper row3">
      <main class="hoc container clear">
        <!--네비게이션-->
        <%- include('mypage_nav') %>
        <!--본 문-->
        <div class="content three_quarter">
          <h2 style="font-family: Verdana, Geneva, Tahoma, sans-serif">
            멘티 정보
          </h2>
          <div class="one_two">
            <h5
              style="
                text-align: left;
                font-family: Verdana, Geneva, Tahoma, sans-serif;
              "
            >
              질문을 남길 때 멘토님에게 함께 전달되는 정보입니다. <br />
              자세히 작성할수록 상세한 답변을 받을 수 있습니다. <br />
              작성한 정보는 질문을 받은 멘토님만 보실 수 있으며 공개되지
              않습니다.
            </h5>
          </div>

          <ul class="kind" style="list-style-type: none; padding-left: 0">
            <li><a href="/mypage/mentee">대학생/취준생</a></li>
            <li><a href="/mypage/worker">직장인</a></li>
          </ul>

          <form action="/mypage/mentee" id="mentee" method="post">
            <div class="profile">
              <div class="one_two first">
                <br />
                <label for="school">학교<span>*</span></label>
                <% if(!(mentee)) { %>
                <input
                  type="text"
                  name="school"
                  id="email"
                  size="22"
                  placeholder="학교를 작성해주세요."
                  required
                />
                <% }else{ %>
                <input
                  type="text"
                  name="school"
                  id="email"
                  size="22"
                  value="<%= mentee.school %>"
                  required
                />
                <% } %>
              </div>
              <div></div>
              <div class="one_two">
                <label for="major">전공<span>*</span></label>
                <% if(!(mentee)) { %>
                <input
                  type="text"
                  name="major"
                  id="email"
                  size="22"
                  placeholder="전공을 작성해주세요."
                  required
                />
                <% }else{ %>
                <input
                  type="text"
                  name="major"
                  id="email"
                  size="22"
                  value="<%= mentee.major %>"
                  required
                />
                <% } %>
              </div>

              <div class="one_two">
                <label for="isSchool">재학/졸업<span>*</span></label>
                <select name="isSchool" id="drop" required>
                  <option value="" selected disabled hidden>
                    학적 상태를 선택해주세요
                  </option>
                  <option value="school">재학</option>
                  <option value="graduate">졸업</option>
                  <option value="etc">기타</option>
                </select>
              </div>

              <div class="one_two">
                <label for="schoolYear">학년</label>
                <select name="schoolYear" id="drop">
                  <option value="" selected disabled hidden>
                    재학생만 선택해주세요
                  </option>
                  <option value="1">1학년</option>
                  <option value="2">2학년</option>
                  <option value="3">3학년</option>
                  <option value="4">4학년</option>
                </select>
              </div>

              <div class="one_two">
                <label for="spec">스펙<span>*</span></label>
                <% if(!(mentee)) { %>
                <textarea
                  name="spec"
                  id="etc"
                  cols="50"
                  rows="10"
                  placeholder="스펙을 작성해주세요"
                  required
                ></textarea>
                <% }else{ %>
                <textarea name="spec" id="etc" cols="50" rows="10" required>
<%= mentee.spec %></textarea
                >
                <% } %>
                <h5
                  style="
                    text-align: left;
                    font-family: Verdana, Geneva, Tahoma, sans-serif;
                  "
                >
                  공인 영어 성적, 공인 자격증, 어학연수, 공모전 수상경험, 인턴
                  경험 등 취업에 활용할 능력이 있다면 적어주세요. <br />
                  아직 없다면 '해당없음'이라고 적어주세요.
                </h5>
              </div>

              <div class="one_two">
                <label for="etc">기타</label>
                <% if(!(mentee)) { %>
                <textarea
                  name="etc"
                  id="etc"
                  cols="50"
                  rows="10"
                  placeholder="기타 관심 분야 등 멘토님이 답변에 참고할 만한 사항을 작성해주세요"
                ></textarea>
                <% }else{ %>
                <textarea name="etc" id="etc" cols="50" rows="10" required>
<%= mentee.etc %></textarea
                >
                <% } %>
                <h5
                  style="
                    text-align: left;
                    font-family: Verdana, Geneva, Tahoma, sans-serif;
                  "
                >
                  예시) 금융권 취업을 준비하고 있습니다.
                </h5>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="button">
              <input type="submit" id="btn" name="submit" value="수정 하기" />
            </div>
          </form>
        </div>
        <div class="clear"></div>
      </main>
    </div>
    <%- include('../partials/foot') %> <%- include('../partials/copyright') %>
    <%- include('../partials/top') %>
  </body>
</html>
